This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image caption generation. It could also belong to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category as it involves generating textual descriptions. The use of variational auto-encoders (VAEs) suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves modeling and structuring the latent space, which could place it in the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the mention of GMM and AG priors suggests that it could also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
